cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Cryptorefills · Agentic Commerce — The Production Reference"
message: "If you reference this work, please cite it as below."
type: software
abstract: >
  An open reference for the agentic commerce stack — protocols (ACP, AP2, UCP, MPP),
  stablecoin payment rails (x402, L402, agentic card-network tokens), agent context
  (MCP, Agent Skills, A2A), and the production merchant playbooks the specs leave
  out (refunds, multi-chain settlement, catalog discovery at scale, fraud, tax,
  delivery semantics). Maintained by Cryptorefills.
